                                            A chemicals and allied products, nec company, Cabot Microelectronics Corp is situated directly at Aurora, IL. It brings in a revenue of $10 million annually and employs 47 people. Cabot Microelectronics Corp's unique nature and offerings are in high demand in the boutique market. The current CEO of the company is William P Noglows.
                                        









